  <!-- §11 How to Use -->
  <h2>How to Use the Yescool Kids Weighted Blanket</h2>
  <ol class="supporting-questions">
    <li>
      <strong>Choose the right weight and age.</strong> The Yescool 3 lb blanket is designed for kids 3–8 years old weighing 30–50 lbs. A good rule: the blanket should weigh about 10% of your child's body weight. Do not use for children under 2 years old or under 20 lbs due to suffocation risk.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Layer it appropriately.</strong> Place the weighted blanket over a regular sheet or duvet cover. This creates a soft boundary and makes washing easier. Never place it directly against bare skin for extended periods, as the texture may feel overwhelming.
