    <li><strong>Appropriate weight for kids:</strong> At 3 lbs, it's neither too heavy nor too light for the 30–50 lb age group. Safe and effective for sensory input.</li>
    <li><strong>Quality construction:</strong> Reinforced seams, durable fabric, and bead containment suggest this blanket will last years with proper care.</li>
    <li><strong>Machine washable:</strong> Unlike many weighted blankets, this one can go in the washing machine (though hand wash is recommended for longevity).</li>
